Reasoning: The paper describes a new programming framework for parallel numerical PDE algorithms operating over distributed meshes. This involves algorithms for mesh distribution, coverings, and duality. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.MS (Mathematical Software), which deals with software for mathematical computation and scientific computing. Other likely sub-categories include cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
